                    <span>This is absolutely the best book ever.The story takes place two years after the book Hatchet, and Brian is told that the government wants him to go back out in the Canadian woods so that he can teach everyone how to survive if stranded in the forest. This time he isn't going alone, a phsycologist named Derek Holtzer is coming to record Brian's every action.Then a thunderstorm comes in... and Derek is struck by lightning and goes into an instant coma. Now Brian must travel down a river on a small raft to a trading post for help. Tofind out more read The River</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">The River</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
